Step 1 :- open command prompt
Step 2 :- type - pip install turtle
step 3 :- open any IDE for eg: Pycharm, visual studio code etc.
Step 4 :- create file
Step 5 :- type - import turtle
Step 6 :- type - t = turtle.Turtle()
Step 7 :- type - t.forward(100)
Step 8 :- type - t.right(90)
Step 9 :- type - t.forward(100)
Step 10 :- Press Run 
